<sect2 id='filters-combine-introduction' lang="en;fr;zh_CN">
  <title lang="en">Combine filters introduction</title>
  <title lang="fr">Introduction aux filtres Combiner</title>
  <title lang="zh_CN">组合滤镜简介</title>

  <indexterm>
    <primary lang="en">Filter</primary>
    <secondary lang="en">Combine</secondary>

    <primary lang="fr">Filtre</primary>
    <secondary lang="fr">Combiner</secondary>
    <tertiary lang="fr">Introduction</tertiary>

    <primary lang="zh_CN">滤镜</primary>
    <secondary lang="zh_CN">简介</secondary>
  </indexterm>
  
  <para lang="en">
    The combine filters associate two or more images into a single image.
  </para>

  <para lang="fr">
    Les filtres Combiner associent deux ou plusieurs images en une seule.
  </para>

  <para lang="zh_CN">
    组合滤镜将两个或多个图像变为一个图像。
  </para>
</sect2>
